<?page title="Tabbox accordion mold UI jumps" contentType="text/html;charset=UTF-8"?>
<zk>
<html><![CDATA[
<p>When opening a tab in accordion/accordion-lite mold, the other tabs below it
           	bumps up and sometimes sticks on it during the animation.(If you can't understand, please contact Simon)</p>
]]></html>
	<window border="normal" width="300px" height="300px" >
		<tabbox height="100%" mold="accordion">
			<tabs>
				<tab label="Tab1" />
